Golden Ridge had a net positive cash flow in the first quarter of 2019 and a net negative cash flow in the second quarter. The goodwill is primarily due to the following:
1. Golden Ridge has been operating under the license of Golden Ridge Rice Mills, LLC since November 2018;
2. Golden Ridge Rice Mills, LLC is currently in the process of consolidating its operations under the license of Golden Ridge Rice Mills, LLC;
3. Golden Ridge Rice Mills, LLC has been in the process of undergoing a substantial change in business model and business strategy;
4. The acquisition of Golden Ridge Rice Mills, LLC has been primarily due to the acquisition of Gold Ridge by Golden Ridge Rice Mills, LLC.
